Oh, my, my, will wonders never cease?

36
00:02:13,090 --> 00:02:14,540
仆人们的早餐摆好了吗
Have you laid the servant's hall breakfast?

37
00:02:14,540 --> 00:02:16,380
好了  帕特莫太太
Yes, Mrs Patmore.

38
00:02:16,470 --> 00:02:17,940
炉子擦亮了吗
And finished blacking that stove?

39
00:02:17,940 --> 00:02:19,220
