You're late when I say you're late.

48
00:03:48,430 --> 00:03:51,250
黛西  你蜷在那儿做什么
Daisy, whatever are you doing there,

49
00:03:51,250 --> 00:03:52,770
黑灯瞎火的
crouching in the dark?

50
00:03:52,850 --> 00:03:53,920
你不在  我也不想用
You weren't here and I didn't like to touch

51
00:03:53,920 --> 00:03:55,650
脏手去拉窗帘
the curtains with me dirty hands.

52
00:03:55,730 --> 00:03:57,270
