At Skelton Park, they've even got it in the kitchens.

57
00:04:07,120 --> 00:04:08,410
为什么呀
What for?

58
00:04:13,330 --> 00:04:15,460
好的  帕特莫太太
Yes, Mrs Patmore.

59
00:04:17,460 --> 00:04:19,060
